Ranger Help for: ambush
=======================

SYNTAX:      ambush <target>
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             underground,mountain,arctic,barren
SLOT COST:   12
BASE SP:     70
SKILL TYPE:  offensive

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to launch a devastating surprise attack
from concealment. The Ranger must be concealed before using this skill.
The sudden, brutal strike catches the target off guard and deals heavy
damage. The effectiveness of the ambush depends on the Ranger's
strength, dexterity, and skill level. Ambush is one of the most
powerful melee attacks available to a Ranger, but it requires careful
preparation and the right conditions to execute.
